OL,5, Tony Blair argued Vladimir Putin should
OL,6, be given a seat at the world's "top    
OL,7, table" despite misgivings from         
OL,8, officials, newly released files reveal.
OL,10,FPapers released by the National        
OL,11,FArchives show in early 2001, the       
OL,12,Fthen-prime minister believed it was    
OL,13,Fimportant to encourage the new Russian 
OL,14,Fpresident to adopt Western values.     
OL,16,FBut officials questioned if the ex-KGB 
OL,17,Fspy could be trusted.                  
OL,19,FFiles also show Mr Putin offered to    
OL,20,Fbuild a gas pipeline to the the UK.    
